Package: entr
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Run arbitrary commands when files change
 The Event Notify Test Runner (entr) runs arbitrary commands when
 files change. Changes are detected through the kqueue/inotify
 kernel interface.
